sub_title: Fourth year Honours student at the Amsterdam School of International Business.
summary: Currently a fourth year Honours student at the Amsterdam School of International Business following a Marketing and Sales major. Over the years, I have developed myself personally and academically in various fields. I continuously look for growth and new opportunities! As a creative and curious person, my passion lies in fashion, people, languages and arts!

awards: [{'title': 'International Project Japan in Amsterdam (2)', 'description': 'Becoming an Honours student guided me on my journey towards self-discovery and enhancement of my skillset. I learned how to communicate appropriately and effectively with people from different cultural backgrounds, in this case with a Japanese background.
